data.description: Welcome to your move-in ready city bungalow located in Bevo Mill w/ 3BR, 2 full bath, & 1370 sq.ft. across 1.5 stories, boasting classic allure w/ arched doorways, period molding, & original wood flooring. Notice the spacious living & dinning rms perfect for entertaining family & friends. The updated kitchen comes fully equipped w/ stylish cabinets, counters, & appliances. A full bath & large bedrm complete ML living. The upstairs boasts 2 spacious bedrms, including the master suite w/ vaulted ceilings, walk in closet & updated full bath. Step outside on the patio w/ pergola overlooking large fenced-in backyard. Add'l features: Newer spray foam installation added, Roof (2020), sewer lateral replaced w/ PVC all the way to city main, zoned-HVAC system w/ programmable thermostat & a heat pump for cost-saving heating/cooling, 3 car parking pad, close proximity to all popular restaurants & shops Bevo Mill has to offer! Welcome home!
